trans-unit.source: Copies the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.Principal"></xref> objects from this <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalCollection"></xref> into the specified array, starting at the specified position index in array.
trans-unit.target: Kopier de <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.Principal"> </xref> objekter fra denne <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalCollection"> </xref> i den angitte matrisen, med Start fra den angitte posisjon indeksen i matrisen.

trans-unit.source: `array` must be one-dimensional.
trans-unit.target: `array`må være endimensjonal.

trans-unit.source: If it is not, an <xref:System.ArgumentException> is thrown.
trans-unit.target: Hvis det ikke er en <xref:System.ArgumentException>forårsakes.</xref:System.ArgumentException>

trans-unit.source: Further exceptions are thrown if the number of elements to copy is greater than the available space from `index` to the end of `array`, if `array` is `null`, or if `index` is less than 0.
trans-unit.target: Ytterligere unntak er oppstår hvis antallet elementer å kopiere er større enn den tilgjengelige plassen fra `index` til slutten av `array`, hvis `array` er `null`, eller hvis `index` er mindre enn 0.

trans-unit.source: Finds the object specified by the given and identityType/identityValue pair from the collection, and returns if the identified was a member of this , and otherwise (in which case the method performs no operation).

trans-unit.source: This function can throw the following exceptions: |Exception|Description| |---------------|-----------------| |<xref:System.InvalidOperation>|This method was called on the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.GroupPrincipal.Members> collection for a domain group, and the domain principal to be removed is a member of the group by virtue of its `primaryGroupId` attribute.| |<xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.NoMatchingPrincipalException>|No principal matching the specified parameters was found.| |<xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.MultipleMatchesException>|More than one principal matches the specified parameters.
trans-unit.target: Denne funksjonen kan throw følgende unntak: | Unntak | Beskrivelse | |---------------|-----------------| | <xref:System.InvalidOperation>| Denne metoden ble kalt for <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.GroupPrincipal.Members>-samlingen for en domenegruppe og sikkerhetskontohaveren for domenet som skal fjernes er medlem av gruppen med virtue i den `primaryGroupId` attributtet. | | <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.NoMatchingPrincipalException>| Finner ingen sikkerhetskontohaver samsvarer med de angitte parameterne. | | <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.MultipleMatchesException>| Mer enn én sikkerhetskontohaver samsvarer med de angitte parameterne.</xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.MultipleMatchesException> </xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.NoMatchingPrincipalException> </xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.GroupPrincipal.Members> </xref:System.InvalidOperation>

trans-unit.source: In theory, this should never happen, because <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalCollection.Add%2A> throws an exception when there is an attempt to add duplicate principals to the collection.
trans-unit.target: I teorien dette bør aldri skje, <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalCollection.Add%2A>oppstår det et unntak når det gjøres forsøk på å legge til duplisert sikkerhetskontohavere i samlingen.</xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalCollection.Add%2A>

trans-unit.source: However, it is possible that another API created the duplicate.| |<xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.ArgumentException>|Thrown when `identityType` is an empty string.|
trans-unit.target: Det er mulig at en annen API opprettet dupliserte. | | <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.ArgumentException>| Et når `identityType` er en tom streng. |</xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.ArgumentException>

trans-unit.source: Copies the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.Principal"></xref> objects from this <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalCollection"></xref> into the specified array, starting at the specified position index in array.
trans-unit.target: Kopier de <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.Principal"> </xref> objekter fra denne <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalCollection"> </xref> i den angitte matrisen, med Start fra den angitte posisjon indeksen i matrisen.

trans-unit.source: `array` must be one-dimensional.
trans-unit.target: `array`må være endimensjonal.

trans-unit.source: If it is not, an <xref:System.ArgumentException> is thrown.
trans-unit.target: Hvis det ikke er en <xref:System.ArgumentException>forårsakes.</xref:System.ArgumentException>

trans-unit.source: Further exceptions are thrown if the number of elements to copy is greater than the available space from `index` to the end of `array`, if `array` is `null`, or if `index` is less than 0.
trans-unit.target: Ytterligere unntak er oppstår hvis antallet elementer å kopiere er større enn den tilgjengelige plassen fra `index` til slutten av `array`, hvis `array` er `null`, eller hvis `index` er mindre enn 0.

trans-unit.source: The T:System.Array that should be populated with <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.Principal"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: T:System.Array må fylles ut med <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.Principal"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: The position in `array` to which the first <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.Principal"></xref> object should be copied to.
trans-unit.target: Posisjonen i `array` som først <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.Principal"> </xref> objektet som skal kopieres til.
